  <brief_title>Efficacy of Combination Therapy for Prevention of Effects of Malaria During Pregnancy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Intermittent Sulfadoxine-Pyrimethamine and Sulfadoxine-Pyrimethamine + Artesunate Treatment in the Prevention of Malaria in Pregnancy in an Area With Chloroquine-Resistant Plasmodium Falciparum</official_title>
